Conditions: TM881: (Taric Measure) Registered imports can be made subject to the retroactive imposition of anti-dumping duties if the investigation on possible circumvention of certain existing anti-dumping measures would result in findings of such circumvention (more information in Commission Regulation (EU) 2017/2300, OJ L 329, p. 39).
